workflow.name: AI-powered multi-channel lead outreach with JotForm, Gemini AI & HeyReach
workflow.description:
# üß† AI-Powered Outreach Engine (Jotform + Gemini AI + HeyReach + Data Tables) ## üöÄ Overview This workflow turns every **Jotform submission** ‚Äî whether from your website or a live marketing campaign ‚Äî into a **fully automated, AI-personalized outreach sequence**. Using **Google Gemini AI**, it instantly generates LinkedIn messages and email content tailored to each lead‚Äôs company and context. Depending on the data provided (like LinkedIn profile or email), it automatically routes the message to the right platform ‚Äî **HeyReach for LinkedIn outreach** or **Gmail for email follow-up** ‚Äî and logs all activity into **n8n Data Tables** for tracking and visibility. The result? Zero manual copywriting, zero campaign setup, and instant activation of every inbound lead through personalized, human-sounding communication. --- ## ‚öôÔ∏è What It Does - **Trigger:** Starts when a new submission is received from a Jotform attached to your website or ongoing campaign. - **Lead Enrichment (Optional):** You can add an enrichment node (like Clearbit) to pull company, role, and domain details. - **AI Message Generation:** - Uses **Google Gemini AI (LangChain)** to write both a **LinkedIn outreach message** and a **short, conversational email**. - Each message is context-aware ‚Äî referencing the company, role, or query captured from the Jotform submission. - **Conditional Routing Logic:** - If the form includes a **LinkedIn URL**, the workflow sends the lead and message to **HeyReach**, adding them to the correct campaign automatically. - If not, it sends the **email variant** via **Gmail**, ensuring no lead is missed. - **Data Tracking:** - All lead details, messages, and campaign statuses are automatically saved into **n8n Data Tables**, creating a single source of truth for your outreach history. - **Result:** Personalized, multi-channel follow-up happens in seconds ‚Äî turning inbound form leads into active, engaged prospects instantly. --- ## üß† Example Use Case Imagine a SaaS or marketing agency running a ‚ÄúRequest a Demo‚Äù or ‚ÄúGet Pricing‚Äù campaign via a Jotform on their website. With this workflow, every time someone fills the form: 1. Their details are captured and stored in **n8n Data Tables**. 2. **Gemini AI** instantly writes a relevant, human-sounding LinkedIn and email message. 3. The lead is automatically added to a **HeyReach campaign** or receives a **Gmail follow-up** if LinkedIn isn‚Äôt available. 4. All statuses (message type, delivery, and timing) are tracked in real time. This workflow replaces hours of manual effort with automated, AI-personalized communication that feels natural ‚Äî not robotic. --- ## üß© Ideal For - **B2B SaaS teams** generating inbound leads through website forms - **Agencies** managing multi-channel LinkedIn + email campaigns - **Sales and growth teams** using form submissions for lead capture - **Marketers** running Jotform-based campaigns looking to instantly activate leads --- ## üí° Key Integrations - **JotForm** ‚Üí Capture and trigger workflow from form submissions - **Google Gemini AI (LangChain)** ‚Üí Generate personalized LinkedIn & Email messages - **HeyReach** ‚Üí Add AI-written messages directly into your LinkedIn campaign - **Gmail** ‚Üí Send AI-personalized cold emails automatically - **n8n Data Tables** ‚Üí Store, monitor, and analyze every lead and message generated --- ## üß† Workflow Logic | Step | Node | Description | |------|------|-------------| | 1 | **JotForm Trigger** | Captures lead data submitted through your form | | 2 | **HTTP Request (Optional Enrichment)** | Pulls company details from Clearbit or any enrichment API | | 3 | **Insert Row (n8n Data Table)** | Stores raw lead submission for tracking | | 4 | **If Node** | Determines if LinkedIn profile URL is available | | 5 | **Google Gemini AI (LinkedIn Agent)** | Creates personalized LinkedIn message | | 6 | **HeyReach Node** | Adds lead + message to selected campaign | | 7 | **Google Gemini AI (Email Agent)** | Generates personalized HTML email | | 8 | **Gmail Node** | Sends the AI-generated email if no LinkedIn is found | | 9 | **Insert Row (n8n Data Table)** | Logs campaign status, sent message, and timestamps | --- ## üßæ Example Output (AI Node) ```json { "To": "alex@company.com", "Subject": "AI automation ideas for CompanyX üöÄ", "Email Type": "LinkedIn or Cold Email", "HTML": "

Hey Alex, noticed CompanyX is scaling fast ‚Äî congrats! üëè

At Amply, we help growing businesses use AI-driven automations to eliminate repetitive ops work and boost team productivity by 30‚Äì50%.

Would it make sense to explore if this could free up your ops bandwidth too?

", "Message": "Hey Alex, noticed CompanyX is scaling fast ‚Äî congrats! üëè At Amply, we help growing businesses use AI-driven automations to eliminate repetitive ops work and boost team productivity by 30‚Äì50%. Would it make sense to explore if this could free up your ops bandwidth too?" }

parameters.content:
his workflow begins with a JotForm submission trigger.  
It captures the following fields submitted through the form:

- **Name**
- **First Name**
- **Last Name**
- **Email**
- **LinkedIn Profile**
- **Company Name**
- **Marketing Budget (in USD)**
- **Domain**
- **Any Specific Query**

You are an expert LinkedIn outreach message creator specialized in B2B SaaS and AI automation services.

Based on the following information, create a personalized, concise, and persuasive LinkedIn message that I can send to key decision-makers (KDMs) such as Operations Heads, CXOs, or Founders.

The message should:

Clearly communicate the value of AI automation as a service (improving efficiency, reducing manual work, cutting costs, etc.)

Avoid sounding like a generic sales pitch ‚Äî keep it conversational and human

Be short enough to be read in under 30 seconds (max 3‚Äì5 sentences)

End with a soft CTA (like ‚Äúopen to a quick chat?‚Äù or ‚Äúworth exploring?‚Äù)

Information to base the message on:
[Insert company name, target industry, and key value proposition here]

Example Output Style

Hey [First Name], noticed your team is scaling fast ‚Äî congrats! üëè
At [Your Company], we help growing businesses use AI-driven automations to eliminate repetitive ops work and boost team productivity by 30‚Äì50%.
Would it make sense to explore if this could free up your ops bandwidth too?

data.details:
The IF node can be used to implement binary conditional logic in your workflow. You can set up one-to-many conditions to evaluate each item of data being inputted into the node. That data will either evaluate to TRUE or FALSE and route out of the node accordingly.

This node has multiple types of conditions: Bool, String, Number, and Date & Time.
